before running the SLKBUILD script (fakeroot slkbuild -X)
libnumbertext have to be installed https://people.salixos.org/djemos/salix/libnumbertext/
apache-ant have to be installed https://people.salixos.org/djemos/salix/apache-ant/
openjdk have to be installed https://people.salixos.org/djemos/salix/openjdk/17.0.3.u7/
After installation can remove openjdk and install openjre which is small in size.
In case build fails REMOVE any previous libreoffice installations.

To build the locale and help packages use the scripts in locale and f folders.
Download Help and Locale packages for your language from 
https://slackware.uk/slackel/x86_64/current/slackel/locale/
and https://slackware.uk/slackel/i486/current/slackel/locale/
